description:
The Silver Card is a good introduction to the Bivreost ecosystem. Explore, participate and become part of a large community! The complete collection includes 600 branded cards. Some benefits for Silver cardholders:

- Exclusive design.
- System avatar for the web extension.
- 25% chance to access the Token Presale on the Bivreost Launchpad.
- Binding and synchronization with Telegram contacts.

A user can have multiple Bivreost Silver Cards.
name: SILVER
